{"name": "odoo14-addon-stock-operating-unit", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-stock-operating-unit", "version": "14.0.1.0.3", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/operating-unit", "license": "LGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-operating-unit", "odoo"], "summary": "Adds the concept of operating unit (OU) in stock management", "upload_time": 1697711861}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-LGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: LGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Foperating--unit-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/operating-unit\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/operating-unit/tree/14.0/stock_operating_unit\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/operating-unit-14-0/operating-unit-14-0-stock_operating_unit\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/operating-unit&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Stock with Operating Units\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:a835ac2236bc107937b6c5734f1a445f2c036c498f92c4fb146cec3c9cd4c16e\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module introduces the following features:\n\n- Adds the operating unit to the Warehouse.\n- Adds the operating unit to the Stock Location.\n- Adds the requesting operating unit to stock pickings.\n- Implements user's security access rules.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n- Assign Operating Unit to Warehouses.\n- Assign Operating Unit to Stock Locations.\n\n## Usage\n\nThis module defines the operating unit entity and the user's security rules.\nOther modules extend the standard Odoo apps with the OU.\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\nThe Manager can see the stock rules of other Operating Units but he can not\nedit them. If he tries to access to one of these stock rules, he will receive\na configuration error.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/operating-unit/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/operating-unit/issues/new?body=module:%20stock_operating_unit%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ForgeFlow\n- Serpent Consulting Services Pvt. Ltd.\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Jordi Ballester Alomar \\<<mailto:jordi.ballester@forgeflow.com>>\n- Aaron Henriquez \\<<mailto:ahforgeflow@forgeflow.com>>\n- Sudhir Arya \\<<mailto:sudhir.arya@serpentcs.com>>\n- Nicola Studer \\<<mailto:nicola.studer@braintec-group.com>>\n- Kitti U. \\<<mailto:kittiu@ecosoft.co.th>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/operating-unit](https://github.com/OCA/operating-unit/tree/14.0/stock_operating_unit) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests", "documentation": ["License LGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_operating_unit", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests..test_stock_operating_unit", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_picking", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests..test_stock_picking", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_security", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests..test_stock_security", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_security", "documentation": ["\u00a9 2019 ForgeFlow S.L.", "\u00a9 2019 Serpent Consulting Services Pvt. Ltd.", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_security.TestStockPicking", "bases": ["test_stock_ou.TestStockOperatingUnit"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_operating_unit.tests.test_stock_security.TestStockPicking.test_stock_ou_security", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Test Security o